  <name>Yum Extender</name>
  <_summary>Graphical package manager</_summary>
  <developer_name>Tim Lauridsen</developer_name>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">@APP_ID@.desktop</launchable>

  <description>
    <_p>
      Yum Extender is a graphical package management application. It allows you to search and browse for packages to install,
      remove and update on your computer.
    </_p>
    <_p>It is designed to give you full control over the packages on your computer and to be used by all users.</_p>
    <_p>Features:</_p>
    <ul>
      <_li>Browse packages available for installation or update</_li>
      <_li>Browse packages installed on your computer</_li>
      <_li>Search packages by name, summary, description</_li>
    </ul>
  </description>

